{"tid":414587,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【李嘉誠拍馬雲】長和夥螞蟻金服組合資 拓支付寶HK","createTime":"2017-09-26T10:44:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T10:55:58.000Z","uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"80e491928e9175cb8ecb55f0ec98c8bb2db96a7c","tid":414587,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T10:44:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170926/large/1506420215_1cc9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170926%2Flarge%2F1506420215_1cc9.jpg&h=7f3d5bc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一直倡議「無現金社會」的阿里巴巴，將與李嘉誠聯手開拓本港電子支付市場！長和（001）公佈，與阿里關聯公司螞蟻金服組成「策略夥伴聯盟」，雙方將組合資企業，共同運營電子錢包「支付寶HK」，進一步整合線上線下的支付服務。<br />\n<br />\n以港幣付款的「支付寶HK」今年5月推出，首兩週吸引逾10萬名活躍用戶使用，現時超過4,000家本港零售商戶提供其掃碼支付服務。合資企業尚待監管機構批准，預計交易於今年底前完成。<br />\n長和聯席董事總經理霍建寧表示，合資企業將提升消費體驗至另一層次。藉長和市場網絡、營商經驗，結合螞蟻金服的科技，料帶來龐大效益，相信長和的電訊、零售和其他客戶可受惠。螞蟻金服首席執行官井賢棟指，公司致力為大灣區居民提供全方位電子金融服務，令用戶生活更便捷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170926/57258498\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170926%2F57258498&d=Fp5P8YFNQeoso2gePw%2BPvBFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=73487811\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170926%2F57258498&h=01f0551c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170926/57258498</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n誠哥都染紅啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8729106175834a4f054afce9a7f881084195b0e","tid":414587,"uid":15815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T10:55:58.000Z","msg":"誠哥小心畀起尾注"}]}